2025-12-11TB, INFCFinancial Administration ActCanada Lands Company Limited's 2025-26 to 2029-30 Corporate Plan and 2025-26 Operating and Capital BudgetsOrder authorizing Parc Downsview Park Inc. to (1) enter into one lease relating to real property that it holds in the Arbo neighbourhood in Toronto, Ontario, having a total value of up to $25,400,000, and retain and use any associated proceeds, if the lease is consistent with activities and projections presented in the corporate plan of Canada Lands Company Limited for the 2025-26 to 2029-30 planning period; and (2) enter into one lease relating to real property that it holds in the Downsview neighbourhood in Toronto, Ontario, at nominal value, if the lease is consistent with activities and projections presented in the corporate plan of Canada Lands Company Limited for the 2025-26 to 2029-30 planning period.N/A
subject: Canada Lands Company Limited's 2025-26 to 2029-30 Corporate Plan and 2025-26 Operating and Capital Budgets
precis: Order authorizing Parc Downsview Park Inc. to (1) enter into one lease relating to real property that it holds in the Arbo neighbourhood in Toronto, Ontario, having a total value of up to $25,400,000, and retain and use any associated proceeds, if the lease is consistent with activities and projections presented in the corporate plan of Canada Lands Company Limited for the 2025-26 to 2029-30 planning period; and (2) enter into one lease relating to real property that it holds in the Downsview neighbourhood in Toronto, Ontario, at nominal value, if the lease is consistent with activities and projections presented in the corporate plan of Canada Lands Company Limited for the 2025-26 to 2029-30 planning period.
